{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"“Castlevania – Grimoire of Souls” Hijrah Ke Smartphone?","content":"<p>Secara pribadi, saya sama sekali tidak kaget atau heran melihat<em> game</em> Castlevania yang kini merambah ke <em>smartphone</em>. Kenapa begitu? Karena Konami.</p>\n<p>Konami sebagai pemilik berbagai IP <em>lovable</em> dan memiliki barisan fans loyal untuk <em>game</em> seperti <em>Metal Gear, Suikoden, Contra,</em> dan masih banyak lagi belakangan ini memang dikenal semakin memfokuskan diri di bidang <em>mobile gaming</em> dan mesin pachinko ketimbang tetap serius di bisnis <em>video game console</em> seperti awal-awal mereka muncul. Langkah ini jelas menuai kecaman dari fans IP Konami yang bernasib antara ‘mati suri’ hingga ‘penanganan asal-asalan’. Frustasinya fans sering terlihat dari meme-meme internet yang kebanyakan berupa hujatan kepada Konami karena mereka tidak mendengarkan suara penggemar.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46871\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46871\" data-attachment-id=\"46871\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania5-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania5-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Ekspresi kekesalan fans Konami dalam meme. Sumber gambar: KnowYourMeme\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ekspresi kekesalan fans Konami dalam meme. Sumber gambar: KnowYourMeme&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania5-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania5-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46871\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania5-1.jpg\" alt=\"Ekspresi kekesalan fans Konami dalam meme. Sumber gambar: KnowYourMeme\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania5-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania5-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46871\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ekspresi kekesalan fans Konami dalam meme. Sumber gambar: KnowYourMeme</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi Konami berkelit saat dituduh tidak serius merawat IP populer mereka. Seperti saat mereka merilis “<em>Metal Gear Survive</em>” untuk meneruskan IP <em>Metal Gear</em>. Walau memecat Hideo Kojima (yang merupakan <em>mastermind</em> dibalik kesuksesan <em>franchise</em> terkenal itu) tapi Konami yakin kalau <em>Metal Gear series</em> bisa terus berjalan walau mereka memecat orang yang menyebabkan <em>Metal Gear</em> terkenal dan dicintai fans.</p>\n<p>Hasilnya? <em>Game Metal Gear t</em>erkini itu disambut dingin oleh pasar dan media. Bahkan oleh barisan <em>fans hardcore</em> <em>Metal Gear series</em> sebelumnya. Mereka semua malah menanti<em> game</em>-nya Hideo Kojima yang akan dirilis ekslusif untuk PlayStation 4 berjudul “<em>Death Stranding</em>”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46872\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46872\" data-attachment-id=\"46872\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania6-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mungkin game Metal Gear yang paling dicibirin oleh fans. Sumber gambar: WccfTech\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mungkin game Metal Gear yang paling dicibirin oleh fans. Sumber gambar: WccfTech&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania6-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania6-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46872\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Mungkin game Metal Gear yang paling dicibirin oleh fans. Sumber gambar: WccfTech\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania6-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania6-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46872\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mungkin game Metal Gear yang paling dicibirin oleh fans. Sumber gambar: WccfTech</p></div></p>\n<p>Bagaimana dengan “Castlevania”?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46869\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46869\" data-attachment-id=\"46869\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania3-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania3-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Wikipedia\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Wikipedia&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania3-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania3-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46869\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Wikipedia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania3-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania3-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46869\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Wikipedia</p></div></p>\n<p>Tokoh dibalik kesuksesan “<em>Castlevania: Symphony of The Night”</em> (1997), Koji Igarashi, memang tidak dipecat oleh Konami. Dia mengundurkan diri dari perusahaan secara baik-baik tahun 2014. Sejak <em>game</em> pertama Castlevania beredar di pasaran Jepang tahun 1986 berjudul “Akumajou Dracula&#8221;, Castlevania selalu dirilis di platform <em>video game</em>; baik <em>home console</em> maupun <em>portable handheld gaming</em>. Belakangan Castlevania merambah medium lain seperti anime (terbaru ada anime keluaran Netflix tahun 2017-2018), <em>mobile gaming smartphone</em> hingga <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/permainan-pachinko-jepang-menuju-kepunahan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mesin pachinko</a>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46867\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46867\" data-attachment-id=\"46867\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania1-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot anime Netflix Castlevania. Sumber gambar: PopNerdTV\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Screenshot anime Netflix Castlevania. Sumber gambar: PopNerdTV&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania1-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46867\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot anime Netflix Castlevania. Sumber gambar: PopNerdTV\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania1-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania1-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46867\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Screenshot anime Netflix Castlevania. Sumber gambar: PopNerdTV</p></div></p>\n<p><em>“Castlevania: Grimoire of Souls</em>” adalah judul terkini dari <em>franchise</em> ini dan ditujukan untuk platform <em>mobile smartphone</em> iOS dari Apple.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46868\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46868\" data-attachment-id=\"46868\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania2-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania2-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Game Castlevania untuk platform mobile smartphone. Sumber gambar: DualShockers\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Game Castlevania untuk platform mobile smartphone. Sumber gambar: DualShockers&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania2-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania2-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46868\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Game Castlevania untuk platform mobile smartphone. Sumber gambar: DualShockers\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania2-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania2-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46868\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Game Castlevania untuk platform mobile smartphone. Sumber gambar: DualShockers</p></div></p>\n<p>Diumumkan pada 17 April 2018, <em>game</em> Castlevania untuk <em>smartphone</em> ini terlihat keren. Selain grafis yang indah, <em>Grimoire of Souls</em> juga akan berisi karakter-karakter (baik protagonis maupun antagonis) yang sudah familiar di kalangan <em>fans game</em> Castlevania sebelumnya. Hal lain yang diumumkan adalah fokus dari <em>game</em> ini yang mengedepankan <em>gameplay</em> kooperatif dan kompetitif dalam format <em>multiplayer</em> via jaringan internet.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46873\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46873\" data-attachment-id=\"46873\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania7-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania7-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania7-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania7-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46873\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania7-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania7-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania7-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46873\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46874\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46874\" data-attachment-id=\"46874\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania8-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania8-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania8-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania8-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46874\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania8-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania8-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania8-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46874\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Menurut <a href=\"http://konami.com/games/castlevania/gos/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website resmi</a>nya <em>game online multiplayer action</em> ini akan menawarkan suasana ‘<em>real-time cooperative action</em>’. Kira-kira mungkin sama seperti <em>game-game mobile</em> populer lain seperti M<em>obile Legend, Arena of Valor</em> atau <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-smartphone-naruto-x-boruto-ninja-voltage-kini-tersedia-untuk-seluruh-region/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Naruto x Boruto: <em>Ninja Voltage</em></a> namun dalam format klasik<em> game</em> Castlevania. Mode permainan yang sudah dikonfirmasi antara lain ‘<em>Fo</em><em>ur-Player Boss Rush</em>’ &amp; ‘4v4 <em>Competitive Multiplayer</em>’.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46875\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46875\" data-attachment-id=\"46875\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania9-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania9-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania9-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania9-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46875\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania9-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania9-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania9-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46875\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Karakter-karakter dari<em> game</em> Castlevania sebelumnya yang sudah dikonfirmasi adalah Simon Belmont, Alucard, Charlotte Aulin, Shanoa dan Maria Renard. Tambahan ada pada dua karakter baru: agen rahasia pemerintah Genya Arikado &amp; peneliti muda seni Anti Dracula bernama Lucy.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46876\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46876\" data-attachment-id=\"46876\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania10-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania10-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania10-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania10-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46876\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania10-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania10-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania10-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46876\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Castlevania:<em> Grimoire of Souls</em> sebenarnya bukan <em>game</em> Castlevania pertama yang menawarkan mode <em>multiplayer</em> seperti ini. Sebelumnya sudah ada mode yang hampir mirip dari <em>game</em> “Castlevania: <em>Harmony of Despair</em>” (2010) yang dulu dirilis melalui toko <em>online</em> Xbox Live Arcade &amp; PlayStation <em>Store</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46870\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46870\" data-attachment-id=\"46870\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: PlayStation Store\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: PlayStation Store&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania4-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania4-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46870\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: PlayStation Store\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania4-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania4-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46870\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: PlayStation Store</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat mengumumkan <em>Castlevania: Grimoire of Souls</em>, Konami tidak menyertakan tanggal rilis resmi namun menjanjikan kalau <em>game smartphone</em> iOS ini akan muncul tahun 2018. Untuk yang tidak sabaran bisa mendaftar di <a href=\"http://konami.com/games/castlevania/gos/cbt/\">http://konami.com/games/castlevania/gos/cbt/</a> sebagai peserta ‘<em>Close Beta Testing</em>’ yang akan dilakukan tidak lama lagi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46877\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46877\" data-attachment-id=\"46877\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/castlevania-grimoire-of-souls-hijrah-ke-smartphone/attachment/castlevania11-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania11-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Polygon&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania11-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania11-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46877\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania11-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber gambar: Polygon\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania11-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/castlevania11-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46877\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Karena Grimoire of Souls ini lebih fokus pada <em>gameplay competitve </em>dan<em> online-centric</em> maka untuk yang berharap kalau <em>game</em> ini memiliki kedalaman cerita seperti yang biasanya ada di <em>game-game</em> Castlevania sebaiknya tidak berharap banyak. Seperti halnya <em>Metal Gear Survive</em>, unsur <em>storyline</em> bukanlah jualan utama. Tapi keseruan bermain <em>online</em> dalam suasana kompetisi <em>multiplayer</em>.</p>\n<p>Sekarang saya ngeri membayangkan seandainya “Genso Suikoden” mengalami nasib yang sama.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a398d98c-58de-5ade-88a5-bb2f80b3e4e3"}}}